    image: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-API-and-Prompts/main/images/poster_case160/output.jpg',
    prompt: `Using the provided reference image, transform the single casual product photo into a polished e-commerce TVC storyboard board for a 15-second ad in 9:16 vertical format, presented as a 9-panel grid. Keep the same blue-and-white ceramic ashtray as the product base, but restage it across cinematic advertising shots with warm premium lighting, shallow depth of field, and a refined lifestyle desktop environment. Add a dark storyboard layout with Chinese titles and timing for each panel.`,
    zh: '将产品照片转换为9:16竖屏15秒TVC广告分镜，9格画面，蓝色青花瓷烟灰缸产品，电影感广告镜头，暖光照明，浅景深，精致生活场景，中国风分镜脚本',
  },
  {
