    prompt: `Luxury Chronograph Watch Ad, hyper-realistic photograph of an elegant chronograph watch on a marble surface, soft studio lighting with subtle reflections, shallow depth of field, gold and silver metallic finish with precision engravings,深邃背景with subtle bokeh, commercial photography style, 8K resolution, photorealistic rendering`,
    zh: '豪华计时码表广告，超写实摄影，大理石表面，柔和影棚光，浅景深，金银金属质感，精细雕刻，柔焦背景，商业摄影风格，8K超清',
  },
  {
    id: 7,
    title: '汉堡产品主图+9格广告',
    category: 'ecommerce',
    author: '@Gdgtify',
    source: 'https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2049449869530775877',
    image: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-API-and-Prompts/main/images/ecommerce_case163/output.jpg',
