    zh: '美食摄影杰作，汉堡放在深色石面上，光泽 brioche 汉堡面包，融化的芝士，脆生菜，番茄，烤牛肉饼，诱人蒸汽，暖侧光，浅景深，高端食品商业风格。15秒美食广告9格分镜脚本',
  },
  {
    id: 8,
    title: 'Galgame风格COS截图',
    category: 'portrait',
    author: '@Zoulinshen',
    source: 'https://x.com/Zoulinshen/status/2045082518089810073',
    image: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-API-and-Prompts/main/images/portrait_case8/output.jpg',
    prompt: `生成一张竖版手机截图风格的图片，整体比例接近9:16。画面中心偏上是一位真人coser扮演二次元角色。画面最上方加入手机系统状态栏UI，画面底部叠加galgame风格对话框，左侧放动漫头像，右侧排版角色名和中文台词。对话框下方加操作栏。整体风格高清、细节丰富，光线柔和。`,
    zh: 'Galgame风格手机截图，真人COSER扮演二次元角色，手机状态栏，底部对话框，动漫头像，角色名，中文台词，操作栏，二次元与真人融合',
  },
  {
    id: 9,
    title: '都市回眸街拍人像',
    category: 'portrait',
    author: '@Tz_2022',
    source: 'https://x.com/Tz_2022/status/2045892003775361198',
    image: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-API-and-Prompts/main/images/portrait_case9/output.jpg',
    prompt: `Urban street photography, turn-back glance portrait, young East Asian woman in casual streetwear, standing on city street at golden hour, natural window light from building reflections, slightly turning head to glance back at camera, candid editorial style, high fashion street look, long coat over casual outfit, cityscape bokeh background with neon signs`,
    zh: '都市街拍，回眸人像，年轻东亚女性，休闲装，金色时刻，城市街道，自然窗光，标志性回眸，街拍风格，长外套，城市霓虹背景',
  },
  {
    id: 10,
    title: '极简空间人像',
    category: 'portrait',
    author: '@iam_miharbi',
    source: 'https://x.com/iam_miharbi/status/2045151354679665101',
    image: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-API-and-Prompts/main/images/portrait_case2/output.jpg',
    prompt: `Cinematic minimal portrait, solitary figure in vast empty space, strong directional light creating dramatic shadows, monochromatic color palette, symmetrical composition, reflective floor surface, moody atmospheric lighting, high contrast black and white with subtle color tint`,
    zh: '电影感极简人像，孤独身影在空旷空间，强烈定向光营造戏剧性阴影，单色调色板，对称构图，反光地板，情绪化氛围照明，高对比黑白带微妙色彩',
  },
